---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout-en.astro';
---

<Layout 
	title="About Peter Rosdahl – Adorable"
	description="Peter Rosdahl runs Adorable – a one-person consultancy for AI transformation and paid social. Experienced in digital marketing since 2016."
	swedishPath="/om"
>
	<main>
		<section class="hero">
			<div class="container">
				<h1 class="hero-title">Hi, I'm Peter Rosdahl.</h1>
				<p class="hero-intro">
					I run Adorable – a one-person consultancy for companies that need senior expertise in paid social and AI transformation without hiring full-time.
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="section">
			<div class="container">
				<h2 class="section-title">Background</h2>
				<p class="text">
					I've been working with digital marketing since 2016. Started with paid social – Meta Ads, LinkedIn, TikTok, YouTube – helping companies actually get a return on their ad spend.
				</p>
				<p class="text">
					In 2023, I started experimenting seriously with AI. Not because it was trendy, but because I saw what it could do. Today I help organizations go from AI-curious to actual implementation.
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="section">
			<div class="container">
				<h2 class="section-title">How I work</h2>
				<p class="text">
					I work with a select few clients at a time, usually when things are a bit unclear. Most of the work happens close to the business – finding the right direction, raising quality, and helping teams make better decisions before they become expensive.
				</p>
				<p class="text">
					The goal is to be close enough to be useful, do the work when it helps, and step back when the team has it covered.
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="section">
			<div class="container">
				<h2 class="section-title">Who I work with</h2>
				<p class="text">
					Creative agencies, tech companies, construction firms, insurance companies, education businesses and more. I work with both B2B and B2C companies. What they have in common is that they need senior expertise – but not a full-time hire.
				</p>
				<p class="text">
					Often it's companies in a growth phase where the right expertise at the right time makes a difference. Sometimes it's established companies that need new expertise for a specific project.
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="section newsletter">
			<div class="container">
				<h2 class="section-title">Newsletter</h2>
				<p class="newsletter-intro">
					I write about AI, digital marketing and what actually works. No sales pitches, just insights from reality.
				</p>
				<a href="https://pr.substack.com" target="_blank" class="newsletter-button">Subscribe via Substack →</a>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="section section-contact">
			<div class="container">
				<h2 class="section-title">Contact</h2>
				<div class="contact-info">
					<p class="contact-name">Peter Rosdahl</p>
					<p><a href="mailto:peter@adorable.se" class="contact-link">peter@adorable.se</a></p>
					<p><a href="tel:+46708235787" class="contact-link">+46 70 823 57 87</a></p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	main {
		background: #fff;
		min-height: 100vh;
	}

	.container {
		max-width: 760px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 0 2rem;
	}

	.hero {
		padding: 8rem 0 4rem;
	}

	.hero-title {
		font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
		font-weight: 400;
		margin: 0 0 2rem;
		line-height: 1.3;
		color: #000;
	}

	.hero-intro {
		font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 2vw, 1.25rem);
		line-height: 1.7;
		color: #000;
	}

	.section {
		padding: 6rem 0;
		border-top: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
	}

	.section-title {
		font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem);
		font-weight: 700;
		margin: 0 0 2rem;
		color: #000;
	}

	.text {
		font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.125rem);
		line-height: 1.7;
		color: #333;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.text:last-child {
		margin-bottom: 0;
	}

	.newsletter {
		background: #fafafa;
	}

	.newsletter-intro {
		font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.125rem);
		line-height: 1.7;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		color: #333;
	}

	.newsletter-button {
		display: inline-block;
		padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
		background: #000;
		color: #fff;
		text-decoration: none;
		font-weight: 500;
		border-radius: 4px;
		transition: opacity 0.2s;
	}

	.newsletter-button:hover {
		opacity: 0.8;
	}

	.section-contact {
		background: #000;
		color: #fff;
		border-top: none;
	}

	.section-contact .section-title {
		color: #fff;
	}

	.contact-info {
		font-size: 1.125rem;
	}

	.contact-name {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.contact-link {
		color: #fff;
		text-decoration: none;
		border-bottom: 1px solid #fff;
		transition: opacity 0.2s;
	}

	.contact-link:hover {
		opacity: 0.7;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.hero {
			padding: 4rem 0 2rem;
		}

		.section {
			padding: 4rem 0;
		}
	}
</style>
